messages.messageBody:
There's a show in England called Changing Rooms that
sounds just like this.
I saw one episode where a woman just hated what they
had done. She didn't get stroppy or anything, but she
cried (she did wait until she thought the cameras
weren't rolling - but they were).
Mostly they did pretty cool stuff, but sometimes it
looked a bit cheesy to me.

Meghan
